coding and decoding program
sample1 answer
letters = [ ]
string = input ("enter a string :")
a = string [: : -1]
for x in a:
   b = ord (x) + 1
   c = chr (b)
   letters.append(c)
print (letters)

enter a string (KDIOSLO)/OUTPUT = (PMTPJEL)

SAMPLE 2 
letters = [ ]
string = input ("enter a string :")
a = string [: : -1]
for x in a:
   b = ord (x) + 1
   c = chr (b)
   letters.append(c)
print (letters)

enter a string (INDIAN)/ output = (OBJEOJ)
